      <li style="border: none">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bplisn.net.cn%2FBookSearch.aspx%3FISBN%3D978-7-5327-4603-3&amp;subject=7532746038&amp;type=borrow&amp;library=10007&amp;link2key=f7ebdf2d40" target="_blank">北京市公共图书馆(3)</a>
